(38, 1, '2017-10-07 19:07:08', '2017-10-07 17:07:08', '<p style="text-align: center;">Pensiamo che creare un’identità on-line e dare visibilità diretta, sia il modo migliore per sponsorizzare le imprese al giorno d’oggi.\r\nLe categorie di impresa a cui ci rivolgiamo sono:</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="csRow">\r\n<div class="csColumnGap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 1.56%;"><img style="border: none;" src="http://business.broovera.it/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png" /></div>\r\n<div class="csColumn brooveracolumns" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 23%;" data-csstartpoint="15" data-csendpoint="236.25" data-cswidth="23.0%" data-csid="c35ea8ce-403a-655f-b0cf-a31eee591342">\r\n<div id="zoomedimages1" class="zmimgs"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-123" src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/mission1-300x153.png" alt="" width="300" height="153" /></div>\r\n<!--\r\n<p style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: bolder; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;">Food &amp; Beverage</p>\r\n-->\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">(Ristoranti, Bar, Pasticcerie/Gelaterie)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="csColumnGap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 1.56%; text-align: center;"><img style="border: none;" src="http://business.broovera.it/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png" /></div>\r\n<div class="csColumn brooveracolumns" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 23%; text-align: center;" data-csstartpoint="251.25" data-csendpoint="472.5" data-cswidth="23.0%" data-csid="12a2a835-7817-b463-843e-5f3ed6295ccb">\r\n<div id="zoomedimages2" class="zmimgs"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-124" src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/mission2-300x153.png" alt="" width="300" height="153" /></div>\r\n<!--\r\n<p style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: bolder; margin-bottom: 0px;"> Wellness &amp; Beauty</p>\r\n-